snippet.title: Star Control®: Origins™ - Gameplay Teaser
snippet.description:
Official Website: https://www.starcontrol.com
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/official.stardock
Twitter: https://twitter.com/starcontrolgame

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Still in early development! Star Control: Origins is a sci-fi action/adventure game with many RPG elements set in the future where the player is the captain of Earth’s first interstellar starship that explores a procedurally created galaxy, makes contact with various alien races, explores unique worlds, and engages in action packed battles, all while trying to unravel the complex intrigue that has the galaxy on the brink of chaos.
